Build and installation
======================

This fork builds with a simple ./build.sh script. Autotools is not used.

Required tools and libraries:

* C23-capable C compiler
* C++20-capable C++ compiler
* pkg-config
* ncursesw
* readline
* curl
* fftw3
* libmpdclient >= 2.8
* taglib C API

Build:

    ./build.sh

Run tests:

    ./build.sh check

Install:

    sudo ./build.sh install

Install under another prefix:

    PREFIX=/opt/ncmpcpp ./build.sh install

Remove build outputs:

    ./build.sh clean

If the working tree still contains files from the old autotools build system,
remove them with:

    ./build.sh prune-autotools
